                "D": "Before each round of battle begins, you will get a certain number of chances to draw <color style='color:#FFCC33'>Combat Units#, <color style='color:#FFCC33'>Formation Banners# and <color style='color:#FFCC33'>Stratagems#.<br>Each round will feature a certain number of opportunities to reset your choices. This will let you replace your current Combat Unit or Stratagem choices when selecting them.<br>The Combat Units, Formation Banners and Stratagems you select will persist until the end of this Wargame."
