                "D": "In Round 3/5/7 of each Wargame, you will gain 1 chance to draw a <color style='color:#FFCC33'>Strategem#.<br>Stratagems can provide various buffs in the Wargame, and choosing them wisely can have a significant impact upon the outcome."
