                "D": "In Round 2/6 of each Wargame, you will gain 1 chance to draw a <color style='color:#FFCC33'>Formation Banner#.<br>After equipping Formation Banners successfully, Combat Units within these squads will be enhanced.<br>In Round 4/8, your Formation Banner(s) will be enhanced."
